DOC.brief_summary: The objective of this study is to collect data on the use of the WIRION system in Patients undergoing Percutaneous Intervention of Saphenous Vein Graft (SVG).
DOC.brief_title: PMS Retrospective Study of WIRION Performance in Patients Undergoing Saphenous Vein Graft (SVG) Intervention
DOC.detailed_description: WIRION system is used as protection device in patients undergoing SVG stenting procedure. This retrospective study collects data on the usability of the WIRION during the procedure.
DOC.criteria: Patients underwent percutaneous intervention (PI) of SVG stenting in which the WIRIONTM system was used. Patient is greater than or equal to 18 years of age. Undergone cardiac surgery in the past 60 days before the procedure.
